eckoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"connection_refused\",\n    \"timeout\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"connection_refused, latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常耗时 22436907.87 ms，connection error 102 次\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"timeout, latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常耗时 23652516.03 ms，Unavailable error\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n总结：大部分问题源于下游 `CartService` 的连接无法建立，以及由此引发的上游组件不可用状态，导致整体服务请求响应时间显著增加。"}
